section.para:
Verification of the login certificate is also disabled as
standard. It can be enabled by setting the &ucsUCRV;
rdp/ignorecertificate to true.

To configure a login-less access to the web interface the &ucsUCRV;
lightdm/autologin/session must be set to XenApp and the
&ucsUCRV; lightdm/autologin to yes.
